The Renaissance Track Club would like to thank each of you
for your participation in our event. We hope you had a great time and
hopefully all of your athletes received their awards. The times in this
meet were measured by a Sprint 8 hand timing machine. There were no wind
meter readings and these times were posted to the best of our ability. If
there are errors, we apologize and vow to continue to try to offer a well
run track and field event. Look for us next year. We will try to get the
same weekend we've had for the last 5 years. We are hoping for the last
Saturday in April 2004. We would like to thank Springco, California Track &
Running News Magazine and Brooks company for their participation in our
event. See you all on the circuit. To all of you - Good Luck and have a
safe and fun season . <> 
(Results are large, and may be slow loading, so give it time...)

Renaissance Relays Results

April 26, 2003
